729149f-a.title: Richmond: Midland Avenue - Colony Avenue
729149f-a.text:
Midland Avenue, at the N.E. corner of Colony Avenue,
showing a bakery and the Midland Department Store occupying
the site. Also shown is a view along the north side of Colony
Avenue.
Sugust 14, 1935.
P.L. Sperr
